{"tid":896476,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"湖南中學校長放 8 部礦機在學校掘礦！最終受到免職處分","createTime":"2018-11-10T05:17:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-10T09:53:41.000Z","uid":51464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"91ba1efd5546f87c455fe01165e3c951fe2316bb","tid":896476,"uid":51464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T05:17:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2205078/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fezone.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2205078%2F&d=gKsu5e2IlVg3nxeHSNKNb1KzBYqMCiHg3GgvTcrvEuQ%3D&h=5db9155a\" target=\"_blank\">https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2205078/</a><br />\n使用區塊鏈（Blockchain）技術的虛擬貨幣掘礦熱潮，隨著近年虛擬貨幣價格下跌和掘礦難度逐漸提升，已經漸漸冷卻下來。中國大陸湖南省有位名為雷華的中學校長，在 2017 年 6 月起開始加入「礦工」行列。為了節省掘礦電費，將多達 8 部礦機放在校園內，以校園的電力掘礦。直至 2018 年 7 月，雷華在校掘礦的事件被發現，最終受到嚴重警告處分和被免職。<br />\n====================================<br />\n香港有無校長咁做？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15fb213488f0347b8440aaa4c022ed78b4ac7363","tid":896476,"uid":198932,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T07:26:49.000Z","msg":"中小學IT狗有間冷氣長開server房平時得佢地會入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12985ca71efa007ea39611a697c5cf572ca4805c","tid":896476,"uid":108266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"15fb213488f0347b8440aaa4c022ed78b4ac7363","tid":896476,"uid":198932,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T07:26:49.000Z","msg":"中小學IT狗有間冷氣長開server房平時得佢地會入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T09:53:41.000Z","msg":"被動收入<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}